sources.title: Solar Attack | Full Movie | Action Sci-Fi Disaster | Mark Dacascos
sources.description:
Solar Attack - The largest coronal mass ejection (CME) ever detected by scientists breaks off from the sun and hurtles toward the Earth. With temperatures soaring higher, the sky on fire and the continued existence of the human race in question, scientists must explode the polar ice caps to stop the CME. Will it backfire or save life as we know it?
2006.  Stars: Mark Dacascos, Joanne Kelly, Kevin Jubinville
